title: How easy was it for patients to contact the out-of-hours GP service by telephone?
analysis_commentary: Of those who did know how to contact the out-of-hours GP service, 80% in 2011/12 said it was easy to contact it by telephone. For the latest survey, July 2014 to March 2015, the value is 77%.
